<p>TeleDirect provides our Healthcare clients with safe and secure policies and procedures coupled with continual staff training and awareness reviews. This includes company-wide trainings regarding information security with emphasis on Personal Health Information (PHI), and the strategies being enabled to mitigate any security issues that may arise. All of these trainings and staff education classes ensure compliance of the related obligations under HIPAA.</p>
<p>Our technology, security, and privacy policies comply with HIPAA standards, such as encryption (SSL), system-user identifiers (logins, passwords), multiple user access levels, high-end physical server security, nightly backups, strong privacy policies, timed log out and comprehensive internal policies.</p>
